1. Use Groovy for all code
2. Use Thymeleaf for all templates
3. Use HTMX for all AJAX requests
4. Use Bootstrap for all styling
5. Use jQuery for all JavaScript
6. Use Spring Boot for all backend code
7. Use PostgreSQL for all database code
8. Use pgvector for all vector database code
9. Use Solr for all search code
10. remember that the controllers are in groovy, and need explicitly defined parameter names due to reflection differences between groovy and java
